title: Walking Trail, Laundry Facilities, Heating
posting_body: ['With quality 1 and 2 bedroom apartments in southwest Denver, Live on South Federal has the perfect layout for you.', 'Our apartments for rent on South Federal Boulevard have on-site laundry facilities, off-street parking, and much more!', 'Visit our amenities page to learn more about our apartment features.', 'Conveniently located near downtown, Live on South Federal Apartments has a wonderful location.', 'Our six properties are easily accessible to popular attractions with proximity to Denver’s main interstates.', 'Call us today to see our apartments!', '-Cable/Satellite', '-Balcony/Patio', '-Ample Closet Space', '-Breakfast Bar', '-Playground', '-Laundry Facilities', '-Courtyard', '-Ceiling Fans', '-Upgraded Kitchen', '-Bike Racks', '-Heating', '-Hardwood Floors', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 8AM-6PM', '2775 S Federal Blvd, Denver, CO 80236', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']
